description: Kentima Holding AB engages in the development, manufacture, and trade of custom-made software and hardware products. The company is headquartered in Staffanstorp, Skane. The company went IPO on 2013-06-19. The firm's products lines include: HMI/SCADA Software, WideQuick, that is a software for creating graphic surveillance and presentation systems; Video Management Software, Ethiris, which is a parent software for camera surveillance; Industrial Computers, Oe, which is a series of industrial computers, and Operator Panels, WideQuick HMI Panel, which is a family of different operator panels that allows users to create a user interface between operator and machine/process section. The firm also provides training courses for its WideQuick and Ethiris products. Its partners include ComDa Te, Entity AB and Griffel AB, among others.
name: Kentima Holding AB (publ)
